casebody.head_matter:
UNITED STATES, petitioner,
v.
Marco HERNANDEZ-LARA.
No. 16-617.
Supreme Court of the United States
May 14, 2018.
On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit. Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit for further consideration in light of Beckles v. United States, 580 U.S ----, 137 S.Ct. 886, 197 L.Ed.2d 145 (2017.).
